data.description: It's Time!  Start living the Dream and planning your vacations in this wonderful gated community!... Boating, Fishing, private beach, beautiful clubhouse and loads of planned activities.  It's all waiting for you here with this spacious 2 bedroom Canterbury model. It’s centrally located on a private street just around the corner from the lake side beach. There’s a full length driveway, spacious size shed and a maintenance free front deck.  It’s being offered fully furnished and comes equipped with lots of cabinets, closets an extra pantry and a large galley style bathroom with linen and vanity cabinetry as well as a convenient laundry bin.   You and yours are all that’s missing!
